Title: Nahm Equations and Boundary Conditions

Authors: Dimitrios Tsimpis

Comments: 5 pages, 1 figure. Minor changes. Two references added. Version to

appear in Physics Letters BJournal-ref: Phys.Lett. B433 (1998) 287-290

We derive certain boundary conditions in Nahm's equations by considering asystem of N parallel D1-branes perpendicular to a D3-brane in type IIB stringtheory.